export default function Logo() {
    return (
        <svg
            width="160"
            height="64"
            viewBox="0 0 160 64"
            fill="none"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            aria-label="Logo Administration DZ"
            role="img"
        >
            {/* Fond transparent */}
            <rect width="160" height="64" fill="white" />

            {/* Croissant rouge stylisé */}
            <path
                d="M30 32c0 11 9 20 20 20 1.5 0 3-.2 4.4-.6-5.8-1.8-10-7.2-10-13.4 0-6.2 4.2-11.6 10-13.4-1.4-.4-2.9-.6-4.4-.6-11 0-20 9-20 20z"
                fill="#D80027"
            />

            {/* Étoile rouge */}
            <polygon
                points="57,20 60,30 71,30 62,36 65,46 57,39 49,46 52,36 43,30 54,30"
                fill="#D80027"
            />

            {/* Texte */}
            <text
                x="80"
                y="40"
                fill="#D80027"
                fontFamily="Arial, sans-serif"
                fontWeight="700"
                fontSize="20"
            >
                Administration DZ
            </text>
        </svg>
    );
}
